### Register User (Auto-creates Company)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyName": "Test Company",
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "password": "Password1!"
}

###

### Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "password": "Password1!"
}

###

### Get My Profile
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/user/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Get My Company
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/companies/my
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Create Workspace (OWNER only)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/workspaces
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Engineering Team",
  "description": "Main engineering workspace"
}

###

### Get My Workspaces
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/workspaces/my
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Create Note (Draft)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/notes
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workspaceId": "{{workspaceId}}",
  "title": "Test Note",
  "content": "This is a test note in draft mode",
  "tags": ["test", "draft"],
  "type": "private",
  "isDraft": true
}

###

### Publish Note (Make Public)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/v1/notes/{{noteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "public",
  "isDraft": false
}

###

### Get Public Directory
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/notes/public-directory?sort=upvotes
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Vote on Note
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/votes
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "noteId": "{{noteId}}",
  "voterUserId": "{{userId}}",
  "type": "up"
}

###

### Get Note History
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/history/note/{{noteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###
